==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Emollient
<hw>E*mol"lient</hw> <pr>(?; 105)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>An external something or soothing application to allay irritation,
soreness, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

